'''植入性胎盤'''（Placenta accreta）是指孕婦在孕期中，[[胎盤|胎盤]]和[[子宫肌层|子宫肌层]]有不正常的緊密附著，可以依胎盤附著或侵入[[子宫|子宫]]程度分為以下的三種：
* 粘連性（Accreta）胎盤：绒毛膜绒毛已穿透子宮內層的{{le|基底蛻膜|Decidua basalis}}，附着到子宫肌层。
* 嵌入性（Increta）胎盤：绒毛膜绒毛侵入子宫肌层。
* 穿透性（Percreta）胎盤：绒毛膜绒毛穿透子宫肌层，影響到其他器官。

因為胎盤異常的附著在子宫肌层，在[[分娩|分娩]]最後要娩出胎盤時，會增加大量出血的風險，常常會需要輸血，若是大量出血到有生命威脅時，會進行[[子宮切除術|子宮切除術]]。
==危險因子==
子宮內的疤痕是植入性胎盤的重要危險因子之一，而[[前置胎盤|前置胎盤]]也是另一個獨立的危險因子<REF>
{{Cite web |url=http://www.mmh.org.tw/obs/highrisk_edu009.htm |title=前置胎盤 |accessdate=2016-10-27 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104125201/http://www.mmh.org.tw/obs/highrisk_edu009.htm |dead-url=no }}
</REF>，其他和有關的危險因子包括懷孕時的年齡、多胎產、之前曾接受過其他子宮手術或是{{le|子宮擴張及搔刮|Dilation and curettage|子宮搔刮}}、子宮曾接觸到輻射、子宮內膜去除、{{le|阿舍曼綜合症|Asherman syndrome}}<ref name="Al Serehi"/>、[[子宮肌瘤|子宮肌瘤]]、子宮異常（uterine anomalies）、[[妊娠高血壓|妊娠高血壓]]及吸煙<ref>[http://www.mababy.com/knowledge/article.aspx?aid=D70D314BAB4F8AE0 健康迎接新生命 「植入性胎盤」不可輕忽！]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

若子宮內有[[疤痕|疤痕]]，也就是{{le|阿舍曼綜合症|Asherman syndrome}}，出現植入性胎盤的比率會變高，子宮內的疤痕一般是因為以往的子宮手術所造成，特別是{{le|子宮擴張及搔刮|Dilation and curettage}}<ref name="Capella">{{cite journal |pages=1230–3 |doi=10.1093/humrep/14.5.1230 |title=Hysteroscopic treatment of severe Asherman's syndrome and subsequent fertility |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_human-reproduction_1999-05_14_5/page/1230 |year=1999 |last1=Capella-Allouc |first1=S. |journal=Human Reproduction |volume=14 |issue=5 |pmid=10325268 |last2=Morsad |first2=F |last3=Rongières-Bertrand |first3=C |last4=Taylor |first4=S |last5=Fernandez |first5=H}}</ref>（用於許多的適應症，像是流產、終止妊娠、產後出血等）、子宫肌瘤切除术<ref name="Al Serehi">{{cite journal |pmid=18946102 |year=2008 |last1=Al-Serehi |first1=A |last2=Mhoyan |first2=A |last3=Brown |first3=M |last4=Benirschke |first4=K |last5=Hull |first5=A |last6=Pretorius |first6=DH |title=Placenta accreta: An association with fibroids and Asherman syndrome |volume=27 |issue=11 |pages=1623–8 |journal=Journal of ultrasound in medicine}}</ref>或是[[剖宫产|剖宫产]]。[[蜕膜|蜕膜]]太薄也可能是造成[[滋胚層|滋胚層]]侵入的原因之一。有些研究指出若胎兒本身是女性，其植入性胎盤的比率會比較高<ref>[http://www.americanpregnancy.org American Pregnancy Association] {{Wayback|url=http://www.americanpregnancy.org/ |date=20060116063059 }} (January 2004) '[http://www.americanpregnancy.org/pregnancycomplications/placentaaccreta.html Placenta Accreta] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060116063059/http://www.americanpregnancy.org/pregnancycomplications/placentaaccreta.html |date=2006-01-16 }}'. Accessed 16 October 2006</ref>。其他容易有植入性胎盤的原因包括低位胎盤、胎盤在子宮前壁（anterior placenta）、先天或是後天的子宮缺陷（例如[[子宮縱隔|子宮縱隔]]）、子宮肌瘤、胎盤異位植入（包括{{le|宮角妊娠|cornual pregnancy}}）等<ref name=labourprac>{{cite book|last=Arulkumaran|first=edited by Richard Warren, Sabaratnam|title=Best practice in labour and delivery|url=https://archive.org/details/bestpracticelabo00warr|year=2009|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=Cambridge|isbn=978-0-521-72068-7|pages=[https://archive.org/details/bestpracticelabo00warr/page/n121 108], 146|edition=1st ed., 3rd printing.}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Bass|first=KE|author2=Morrish, D |author3=Roth, I |author4=Bhardwaj, D |author5=Taylor, R |author6=Zhou, Y |author7= Fisher, SJ |title=Human cytotrophoblast invasion is up-regulated by epidermal growth factor: evidence that paracrine factors modify this process.|journal=Developmental Biology|date=August 1994|volume=164|issue=2|pages=550–61|pmid=8045351|doi=10.1006/dbio.1994.1223}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Shimonovitz|first=S|author2=Hurwitz, A |author3=Dushnik, M |author4=Anteby, E |author5=Geva-Eldar, T |author6= Yagel, S |title=Developmental regulation of the expression of 72 and 92 kd type IV collagenases in human trophoblasts: a possible mechanism for control of trophoblast invasion.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-obstetrics-and-gynecology_1994-09_171_3/page/832|journal=American Journal of Obstetrics and Gynecology|date=September 1994|volume=171|issue=3|pages=832–8|pmid=7522400|doi=10.1016/0002-9378(94)90107-4}}</ref><ref name=acog>{{cite journal|last=ACOG Committee on Obstetric|first=Practice|title=ACOG Committee opinion. Number 266, January 2002 : placenta accreta.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_obstetrics-and-gynecology_2002-01_99_1/page/169|journal=Obstetrics and gynecology|date=January 2002|volume=99|issue=1|pages=169–70|pmid=11777527|doi=10.1016/s0029-7844(01)01748-3}}</ref>。

若產婦超過35歲，曾作過[[剖宮產|剖宮產]]，目前子宮內有疤痕，且前置胎盤恰好蓋在疤痕上，其出現植入性胎盤的機率為40%<ref>{{cite book|last=Hobbins|first=John C.|title=Obstetric ultrasound : artistry in practice|year=2007|publisher=Blackwell|location=Oxford|isbn=978-1-4051-5815-2|pages=10}}</ref>。

==病因==
植入性胎盤是指胎盤和子宫肌层不正常的緊密附著，可能是因為子宮內沒有形成{{le|蜕膜基底|decidua basalis}}或是{{le|尼塔布赫层|Nitabuch's layer}}發育不完全所造成<ref name=gabbe>{{cite book|editor1=Steven G. Gabbe|editor2=Jennifer R. Niebyl|editor3=Joe Leigh Simpson|title=Obstetrics: normal and problem pregnancies|url=https://archive.org/details/gabbeobstetricsn00gabb|year=2002|publisher=Churchill Livingstone|location=New York, NY [u.a.]|isbn=9780443065729|pages=[https://archive.org/details/gabbeobstetricsn00gabb/page/n1051 519]|edition=4.}}</ref>。

